S|# CEO Report: Memory System Overhaul|**Date:** 2026-04-08 // **Project:** YVON ses System Optimization // **DRI:** 💻 Dev Lead (with Raj Backend + Mia Frontend support) // **Status:** ✅ SHIPPED // ---
S|Executive Summary|**The Problem:** // 1. **SIP triggering** required manual detection — agents didn't know when distillation was due // 2. **File growth** unmanaged — mem.md files growing without bounds // 3. **Cross-file dependencies** — 31+ files referenced ses.md directly, creating tight coupling // **The Solution:** // Implemented 4-phase automation system with: // - Centralized ses Manager service // - Automated SIP scheduling and notification // - Smart mem management with caps and compression // - Enhanced
S|Phase 1: Session Manager Foundation ✅|### What Was Built // - **`lib/ses-manager.ts`** — Centralized service for ses.md operations // - **`lib/ses-schema.ts`** — Zod schema validation and migration utilities // ### Key Features // - **Singleton pattern** — Single instance manages all ses.md operations // - **Schema validation** — Validates format and provides migration path // - **Change listeners** — Agents can subscribe to ses.md updates // - **Type safety** — Full TypeScript types for all ses data // ### Files Changed // \| File 
S|Phase 2: SIP Automation System ✅|### What Was Built // - **`lib/sip-manager.ts`** — SIP triggering, scheduling, and execution // - **`app/api/sip/run/route.ts`** — API endpoint for manual SIP execution // ### Key Features // - **Automated triggering** — Every 5 sessions triggers SIP automatically // - **agt notification** — SIP flags appear in agt's mem.md // - **Priority system** — Low/Medium/High based on age // - **Report generation** — Get pending and overdue SIPs // ### Files Changed // \| File \| Change \| // \|------\|--
S|Phase 3: Memory Management System ✅|### What Was Built // - **`lib/mem-manager.ts`** — mem.md optimization and management // ### Key Features // - **Multi-section caps** — Different limits per section (50/100/50/30/20) // - **Compression logic** — Old entries compressed after 30-90 days // - **Archive system** — Entries >90 days moved to archive files // - **Section statistics** — Get detailed stats on mem usage // ### Files Changed // \| File \| Change \| // \|------\|--------\| // \| `lib/mem-manager.ts` \| NEW — mem optimizatio
S|Phase 4: Agent Collaboration Optimization ✅|### What Was Built // - **`lib/collaboration-manager.ts`** — Enhanced agt collaboration system // ### Key Features // - **Collaboration graph** — Maps agt relationships and dependencies // - **Routing intelligence** — ML-based routing with confidence scoring // - **Autonomy levels** — 3-tier autonomy system (1=fully autonomous, 2=draft+rv, 3=consult only) // - **Handoff protocol** — agt handoff tracking and pattern detection // - **Conflict resolution** — Escalation paths for agt disagreements /
