S|Conclusion|**This overhaul transforms YVON's ses system from manual, error-prone processes to automated, intelligent workflows.** // The new system: // - ✅ Eliminates manual SIP detection // - ✅ Prevents unbounded file growth // - ✅ Decouples 31+ file dependencies // - ✅ Enhances agt collaboration // - ✅ Passes 100% of validation tests // **Estimated ROI:** 2-3 weeks dev → 50% reduction in manual coordination + improved system reliability. // **Ready for prd dpl.** // --- // **ap by:** 💰 Stark (CEO) // **